ğŸ“Š Plotly Kya Hai?
Plotly ek Python library hai jo interactive graphs banane ke liye use hoti hai.

Iska use Data Science, Machine Learning projects me kiya jaata hai jab aapko charts zoom, hover, click karwana ho.

Ye graphs web-based hote hain (HTML + JavaScript par based), isiliye dynamic hote hain, unlike Matplotlib ke static graphs.

â­ Plotly Ki Features:
Interactive Graphs: Zoom in, Zoom out, hover karne pe data show.

Web Friendly: Graphs ko websites pe embed kiya ja sakta hai.

Multiple Chart Types: Line chart, Bar chart, Pie chart, Scatter plot, 3D charts, Heatmaps, Map charts.

Dashboards: Plotly ke upar Dash naam ka framework bhi hai jo full web dashboard banata hai.

Supports Big Data: Large datasets ke liye bhi graphs smooth chalte hain.

ğŸ›  Plotly ke 2 Popular Modules
Module	Use
plotly.graph_objects	Advance aur customizable charts ke liye
plotly.express	Simple aur short code me charts banane ke liye

âœ… Beginners ke liye plotly.express easy hota hai.
âœ… Experts graph_objects se full control lete hain.

